# UI Components

This project uses [Shadcn UI](mdc:https:/ui.shadcn.com) which is built on top of Radix UI and Tailwind CSS. The components are located in the `/components/ui` directory.

## Key UI Components
- Buttons, inputs, forms, and other basic UI elements
- Cards for content organization
- Dialog and modals for interactions
- Tables for data display

## Usage Example
```tsx
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
import { Input } from '@/components/ui/input';
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '@/components/ui/card';

// Component using UI elements
function MyComponent() {
  return (
    <Card>
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle>Form Title</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <Input placeholder="Enter value" />
        <Button>Submit</Button>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
}
```

The components are configured in [components.json](mdc:components.json) and use Tailwind CSS for styling.

